<div class="en es de fr pt tr vi id pl it">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 580" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="28" fill="#fafafa" font-size="14" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Why the Shape of Cycle Tops Changed — the Growth of the Options Market</text>
  <text x="20" y="48" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">Same "top," different curve — depending on the size of options open interest</text>
